name: Woke
description: $WOKE is the only currency that increases in value every time someone gets offended on the internet. $WOKE isn't just a cryptocurrency; it's a revolution wrapped in a blockchain, sprinkled with fairness, and served on a platter of inclusivity. It's the only currency that checks its privilege at every transaction and apologizes for its carbon footprint with every transfer. With $WOKE, you're not just investing in a currency; you're investing in a statement that says, "I'm financially savvy and morally superior.
